snippet.title: Miranda Cosgrove REACTS To Drake Bell's Official Sentencing *IG LIVE*
snippet.description:
Miranda Cosgrove REACTS To Drake Bell's Official Sentencing *IG LIVE*
Lots of dark truths about television stars have been brought to light recently, but over the past couple of years, it seems that past Nickelodeon stars have more dark truths coming to light than any others. For quite some time, Drake Bell was in the spotlight for several reasons and as time continued on, he slowly found himself getting into more and more trouble. Over the years, Drake Bell has not had the best of reputations and it just seems that his reputation is facing quite a lot of trouble. The former Nickelodeon star, who goes by the name Drake Campana has just been sentenced and what has followed does not look all too good.
